Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pop-up doll,\Nand broken ceramic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery-solving logic is helpful\Nagainst people's dry hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is an exciting first errand!\NExhilaration turns into terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the\Nsingle truth for what it is--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:57.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The First Errand Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The First Errand Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:26.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Shopping Street--\NFirst Errand Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad it's sunny out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Group #1 has just left Beika Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What place will the Junior\NDetective Club's own Wataru-{\i1}kun {\i0}get?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get good shots, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Don't get left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids'll be kids. Go get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Act more enthusiastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shopping street has\Nsome of your biggest clients!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we accept this job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the public will love us!\NWe asked really hard for the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So we asked for the job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with that, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of such\Na detective group...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru-{\i1}kun {\i0}has just passed\Nthe vegetable store! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he can't buy a {\i1}daikon{\i0}!\NWhat will come of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Junior Detective League was\Nput in charge of recording the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would later be aired on local TV,\Nand the children would get prizes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,depending on their rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple.\NGo alone from Beika Park
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to Beika Shopping Street,\Nsome 500 meters away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,buy the items on\Nthe shopping list, and return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no parents or onlookers\Ncan talk to or help them--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they can only watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's actually tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some kids keep coming back\Nto ask their mothers for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some kids get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some buy toys and\Ncandy for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and some spend all\Ntheir time in arcades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are kids too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His group's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0};\Nhe lives in my neighborhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't started yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's playing by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s items are a toothbrush,\Nfried tofu, and a {\i1}shugi-bukuro{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a {\i1}shugi-bukuro{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bag for kings,\Nbishops, and pawns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 'shogi'! (chess)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Maybe you should enter too!\NIt'd be a good match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have gotten far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This area is near your house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that\Nhis house is also nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,went home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that.\NHiroshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}is a loner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So was I. I often\Nplayed alone, just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own home, or nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}. Does he often\Nplay alone around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The empty lot!\NHe's always playing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bicycle track!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fresh, and suddenly gets deeper.\NIt must've gotten heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}got on the back of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He waved and ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he playing a joke on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned building?\NWhat was he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing by himself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally at the shopping street!\NWill he be able to do his errands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First is the toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He has to buy\Nthe toothbrush here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's gonna get\Nthe fried tofu first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Someone cut this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing,\NConan?! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stationery shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he buying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One {\i1}shugi-bukuro{\i0}, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. That'll be 200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a {\i1}shugi-bukuro{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pure luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two left! What will he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I put the side brake on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rope and this car!\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we lose him again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you weren't filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone out to get\NHiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Hiroshi's Yaiba figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally started his errands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He treasures this figure.\NIt's weird for him to just leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he didn't go of his\Nown accord! He was taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! But someone tried\Nto kill him in fake accidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they failed twice, so then--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is just a theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure they'd believe us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's find Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can call the police!\NI hope I'm wrong, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not that way, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go to the cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! If he is being targeted, then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that'll tell us where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta. Mitsuhiko. Play back all\Nyour footage of Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they tape something suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Go back a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play that part again and pause it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely. In Genta's camera,\Nhe looks like he's waving at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but in Mitsuhiko's camera--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A curb mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Hiroshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}was waving at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More precisely, at a reflection\Nof something in this mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The window!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was waving to\Nsomeone in that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NHe didn't stop here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had some kind of reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what does that have to do\Nwith him being kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Danger- Building Demolition
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demolition is today!\NWe don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll go in alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Junior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful-- the floor is fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem to be in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means nobody's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go downstairs, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A basement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he's down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hiroshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}dead too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An anesthetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was kidnapped and\Nbrought here... by the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is a dead body doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer planned to make the\Nmurder look like a demolition accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first floor was fragile;\Nif any debris fell during the demolition,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the basement would be wrecked.\NThat was the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from his actions, I doubt\Nhe witnessed the actual murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the killer didn't\Nknow how much he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they ran ahead\Nto the shopping street--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer eventually decided\Nto fake his death too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty smart\Nfor a couple of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to kill us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking them so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-{\i1}kun {\i0}isn't back yet, either.\NWhat could they be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably loitering around\Nsomewhere. Kids'll be kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this done quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. It won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you\Nwouldn't call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one\Nwho wanted to come in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The demolition's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running water? Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might survive, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying!\NThey'll come back! Kids'll be kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if something bad\Nhas happened to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pulling so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Junior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've been crushed\Nalong with that dead body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to the weak support struts,\Nthe basement wall crumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, it led right\Ninto an underground tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! You have another store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried tofu and one toothbrush, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That was your\Nconvenience store, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dirty stockbroker tricked me,\Nand I racked up more debt
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than I could ever pay off,\Nand my family ran out on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that\Nstockbroker that I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My store was\Nrepossessed and shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't as popular as stores\Non the shopping street--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be quickly forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0} remembered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to buy from\Nyour store for his first errand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very same Hiroshi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}that you tried to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, little boy! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge victory for the\NJunior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's what happened? Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess kids'll be kids. How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have a bath, some booze,\Nand get some shut-eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's Hiroshi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were his last two things again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, fried tofu and--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's go,\NJunior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:24:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck am I doing?\NWhy am I stuck doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you looking at, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching that\Napartment's veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She jumped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a murder!\NMeaning the most suspicious person is--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--the guy on the phone\Nwho told her not to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how could he do it\Nfrom so far away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrator Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.22,0:24:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrator Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.75,0:24:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.21,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact Lens Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.82,0:24:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is a little grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.87,0:24:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun, you're not allowed to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.02,0:24:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
